Fed up of people coming along and triggering the de_cpl_mill exploit on your server?
You NEED this version! ;)

The bsp is still named de_cpl_mill and can replace the default version on your server.
This will REMOVE the stupid low-grav exploit.
Clients DO NOT need to download the new version.
